			<div class="dablink">This article is about adherents of Sikhism.  For town in Kedah, Malaysia, see <a href="/wiki/Sik,_Kedah" title="Sik, Kedah">Sik, Kedah</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox" style="width:22em; background:#fff6d9; text-align:center; font-size:95%;" cellpadding="2">
