ਸਿੱਖ</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border:none; padding:0.6em 0 0 0;"><a href="/wiki/File:Punjab_flag.svg" class="image" title="Punjab flag.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4f/Punjab_flag.svg/100px-Punjab_flag.svg.png" width="100" height="67" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border:none; padding:0.6em; line-height:11pt; font-size:95%;">The <a href="/wiki/Nishan_Sahib" title="Nishan Sahib">Nishan Sahib</a>, flag of the <a href="/wiki/Sikhs" title="Sikhs" class="mw-redirect">Sikhs</a></td>
</tr>
